OL,6,FA delivery driver, Robert Dyer, tried
OL,7,Fto help Mr Cole but was also overcome
OL,8,Fby the gas. They were both then
OL,9,Frescued, and while Mr Dyer quickly
OL,10,Fregained consciousness, Mr Cole died
OL,11,Fin hospital on Christmas Day.
OL,13,FAn inquest concluded that, on the
OL,14,Fbalance of probabilities, hydrogen
OL,15,Fsulphide had contributed to Mr Cole's
OL,16,Fdeath.
