OL,6,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,7,Finvestigation found that Futamura
OL,8,FChemical (UK) Ltd had not adequately
OL,9,Frisk assessed its production process,
OL,10,Fas it failed to identify that hydrogen
OL,11,Fsulphide gas, a by-product of the
OL,12,Fmanufacturing process, could enter the
OL,13,Fsite's water effluent system.
OL,15,FThe inquest heard that while Futamura
OL,16,FChemical had implemented control
OL,17,Fmeasures for hydrogen sulphide in the
OL,18,Fproduction area, it did not adequately
OL,19,Fassess the risks of hydrogen sulphide
OL,20,Fbuilding up in the drainage system.
