OL,6,FThis could lead to the gas being
OL,7,Freleased from the drains.
OL,9,FSymptoms of exposure to the gas
OL,10,Finclude dizziness, loss of
OL,11,Fconsciousness, eye irritation, and
OL,12,Fdeath.
OL,14,FFutamura Chemical UK Ltd pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to breaching two health and
OL,16,Fsafety at work regulations. On January
OL,17,F6 2026 the company was fined #200,000
OL,18,Fand ordered to pay #20,000 in costs at
OL,19,FWarrington Magistrates' Court.
