OL,6,FHSE Inspector Matthew Shepherd said:
OL,7,F"This tragic case shows the importance
OL,8,Fof conducting a thorough and robust
OL,9,Frisk assessment to ensure that all
OL,10,Frisks are properly identified and
OL,11,Fmanaged.
OL,13,F"Where companies use, or produce
OL,14,Fwithin their processes, substances
OL,15,Fharmful to health, it is vital that
OL,16,Fthey have fully considered and
OL,17,Fcontrolled all pathways to exposure.
OL,18,FFailure to do so can have terrible
OL,19,Fconsequences."
