OL,6,FA Futamura spokesperson has since
OL,7,Fsaid: "Futamura was deeply saddened by
OL,8,Fthe death of Alexander Cole, whom we
OL,9,Fknew as Alec.
OL,11,F"Alec was a well-liked, respected and
OL,12,Flong serving member of our close-knit
OL,13,Fteam and his death has had a profound
OL,14,Feffect on both the directors and staff
OL,15,Fof the company. The company wishes to
OL,16,Fexpress once more its sympathies to
OL,17,FAlec's family and friends.
