OL,6,F"Futamura pleaded guilty to 2 charges,
OL,7,Funder the Health and Safety at Work
OL,8,Fetc Act 1974, of failing to protect an
OL,9,Femployee and failing to protect a
OL,10,Fcontractor so far as reasonably
OL,11,Fpracticable. The company was fined
OL,12,F#200k and is required to pay costs to
OL,13,Fthe Health and Safety Executive.
